      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先搭建主体：边缘节点指向静止，静止和运动双向连接，运动指向Crash。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
